  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nconcurrent.futures.process._RemoteTraceback:\r\n\"\"\"\r\nTraceback (most recent call last):\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/.pyenv/versions/3.6.3/lib/python3.6/concurrent/futures/process.py\", line 175, in _process_worker\r\n    r = call_item.fn(*call_item.args, **call_item.kwargs)\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/sites/py-evm/p2p/p2p_proto.py\", line 56, in decode\r\n    raw_decoded = cast(Dict[str, int], super(Disconnect, self).decode(data))\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/sites/py-evm/p2p/protocol.py\", line 85, in decode\r\n    return self.decode_payload(data[1:])\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/sites/py-evm/p2p/protocol.py\", line 72, in decode_payload\r\n    data = rlp.decode(rlp_data, sedes=decoder)\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/python-environments/trinity/lib/python3.6/site-packages/rlp/codec.py\", line 220, in decode\r\n    obj = sedes.deserialize(item, **kwargs)\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/python-environments/trinity/lib/python3.6/site-packages/eth_utils/functional.py\", line 22, in inner\r\n    return callback(fn(*args, **kwargs))\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/python-environments/trinity/lib/python3.6/site-packages/rlp/sedes/lists.py\", line 84, in deserialize\r\n    raise ListDeserializationError('List has wrong length', serial)\r\nrlp.exceptions.ListDeserializationError: List has wrong length\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nThe above exception was the direct cause of the following exception:\r\n\r\nTraceback (most recent call last):\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/sites/py-evm/p2p/peer.py\", line 739, in connect\r\n    self.cancel_token)\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/sites/py-evm/p2p/peer.py\", line 143, in handshake\r\n    await peer.do_p2p_handshake()\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/sites/py-evm/p2p/peer.py\", line 222, in do_p2p_handshake\r\n    cmd, msg = await self.read_msg()\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/sites/py-evm/p2p/peer.py\", line 324, in read_msg\r\n    token=self.cancel_token)\r\n  File \"/Users/piper/sites/py-evm/p2p/cancel_token.py\", line 110, in wait_with_token\r\n    return done.pop().result()\r\nrlp.exceptions.ListDeserializationError: List has wrong length\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis error occurs semi-regularly during fast sync.\r\n\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nExplicit error handling.\r\n",
